If you'd like to help us make Oxygen or contribute in any way please join the telegram channel https://t.me/OxygenSquared.chat or send a mail to (info@oxygen-design.org) or (nuno@nuno-icons.org). One of the team members is almost always online. We'd love to to discuss the possibility with you :-)

In order to coordinate the addition of icons to the theme itself, all external artists should send their work for review to one of the referred emails, they will be reviewed for  licensing of the theme and the compatibility with the guidelines for creating Oxygen icons.

NOTE:
Contributors should realize that the Oxygen icon theme maintainers can (and probably will) modify, delete, reuse contributed artwork.

The Oxygen Team
